{"word":"G1266 - διαμερίζω - diamerízō - dee-am-er-id'-zo - Cloven","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαμερίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diamerízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-am-er-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cloven</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பங்கிடு, பிரிந்திரு, பகிர்"},{"paragraph":"to divide, to cleave asunder, to cut in pieces, to distribute"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G3307 - μερίζω - merízō - mer-id'-zo/3307\">G3307</a>; to <i>partition thoroughly</i> (literally in distribution, figuratively in dissension): - cloven, divide, part.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}